# ICAO Delta

The `flight-manual/` directory is the only authoritative documentation.

Before implementing or refactoring any feature:

1. Read the relevant Flight Manual section.
2. Verify that implementation matches documentation.
3. If implementation changes intended behavior, update the Flight Manual in the same PR.

Never create parallel documentation unless explicitly requested.

Never duplicate product decisions outside the Flight Manual.